WEBVTT

00:00.992 --> 00:03.228
Kids,
Barney's mom had this blouse

00:03.229 --> 00:05.363
<i>that she absolutely loved,</i>

00:05.365 --> 00:07.031
<i>but then Robin won it</i>
<i>in a poker game,</i>

00:07.033 --> 00:09.200
<i>which led</i>
<i>to some slight awkwardness.</i>

00:09.202 --> 00:13.070
You won the battle...
but I'll win the war.

00:13.072 --> 00:14.906
Game on, bitch.

00:14.908 --> 00:18.459
<i>Please, Mom,</i>
<i>I need you to just be cool.</i>

00:18.461 --> 00:20.011
Okay, can you do that for me?

00:20.013 --> 00:21.078
For you, yes.

00:21.080 --> 00:22.579
And for Robin?

00:22.581 --> 00:23.965
She's gonna be

00:23.967 --> 00:25.916
your daughter in 33 hours.

00:25.918 --> 00:26.884
Daughter in <i>law.</i>

00:26.886 --> 00:28.135
Making it illegal

00:28.137 --> 00:30.137
for you not
to treat her like a daughter.

00:30.139 --> 00:31.856
In-lawyered.

00:32.473 --> 00:33.757
Please, Mom.

00:33.759 --> 00:36.527
All Robin wants to do is
put this whole thing behind her

00:36.529 --> 00:39.397
so she can get married and
put this whole thing behind her.

00:39.399 --> 00:41.282
Ah! Get-this-over-with-quickly
so-we-can

00:41.284 --> 00:44.201
move-past-how-awkward-it-was
that-I-just-said-that five!

00:44.203 --> 00:46.370
Fine. If Robin's ready
to bury the hatchet,

00:46.372 --> 00:49.040
then I guess
I'm ready to bury the hatchet.

00:49.042 --> 00:51.742
Morning, bitches.
Like my new blouse?

00:51.744 --> 00:53.744
Oh, hell, <i>no!</i>
No, Mom. Mom!

00:53.746 --> 00:54.996
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

00:58.417 --> 01:02.417
<font color=#00FF00>♪ How I Met Your Mother 9x08 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Lighthouse</font>
